{"tid":520543,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺玩Sarahah嘅人都以為自己受歡迎？","createTime":"2018-01-05T14:05:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-19T06:44:14.000Z","uid":155674,"like":58,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ee69ecdab82769f0c36184d2f0dc6272a0126f23","tid":520543,"uid":155674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T14:05:17.000Z","msg":"身邊有幾個港女狗公朋友都有係IG post呢個網，<br />\n本身都以為又係收兵溝女手段，<br />\n話就話留真心話問問題，<br />\n點知到最後又係公佢贏 字我輸嘅道理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n本身見到隻狗公係咁po story回覆啲人嘅問題都冇乜野，<br />\n之後發覺唔對路喎，<br />\n有乜理由全部都係讚佢，<br />\n明明中學啲朋友不論男女都好憎佢。<br />\n之後有幾個朋友就留言就笑佢中學狗公嘅事，<br />\n睇下佢點回應。<br />\n<br />\n點知佢突然發脾氣，<br />\n開個story屌人話唔好係度鬧佢侮辱佢，<br />\n我一睇到差啲笑到收唔到聲。<br />\n唔通全世界都鐘意佢咩，<br />\n又要叫人地留真心話，<br />\n又要屌人地留真心話，<br />\n仲要搏埋其他人同情。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申，個狗公中學冇溝過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e33faf50a4f7b749e5f0e54f36e748e96d8fee96","tid":520543,"uid":155674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T14:11:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16687d6117cd7a10ee9b8f052318f56332dbf012","tid":520543,"uid":155674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T14:14:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a61127e68f857dadf40d1aeccf4117d0e662919","tid":520543,"uid":155674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T14:15:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"051b10e9e12748a9218ea396f1ec265654280826","tid":520543,"uid":10274,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T14:18:58.000Z","msg":"真係好多港女玩lee個網<img src=\"/assets/fac